De Ringbrug en de Sint Maartensbrug word:
The Ringbrug and the Sint Maartensbrug are operated locally.
The bridge is not operated when visibility is insufficient.
Outside the set operating times the bridges are not opened. In the following circumstances, opening of the bridges is postponed:
- in strong winds (the criterion is wind force 7 Bft);
- in dense fog (when the nautical operator can no longer see the barriers);
- during maintenance work that cannot be interrupted;
- during established closures.
